# CRAG Database Skill

Use the CRAG database environment variables to inspect available databases before making changes.

- SQL databases expose `DATABASE_KIND`, `DATABASE_URL`, `DATABASE_NAME`, `DATABASE_USER`, and when available `DATABASE_HOST`, `DATABASE_PORT`, and `DATABASE_PASSWORD`.
- SQLite exposes `DATABASE_PATH`.
- Vector stores expose `VECTOR_KIND`, `VECTOR_COLLECTION`, `VECTOR_PERSISTENCE_PATH`, and optionally `VECTOR_URL`.
- Run `python3 $CRAG_RUNTIME_DIR/skills/{{ skill_name }}/list_resources.py` to list SQL tables or vector collections.
